    <title>Linux下常用的压缩工具和常用操作</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2018/03/12/Linux%E4%B8%8B%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%8B%E7%BC%A9%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E5%92%8C%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2018/03/12/Linux下常用的压缩工具和常用操作/</id>
    <published>2018-03-12T09:14:15.917Z</published>
    <updated>2018-03-12T09:14:15.913Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本文在这里对Linux下一些比较常见的压缩文件格式的工具，给出它们简单、经常使用的部分操作。参考了<br><a href="https://linux.cn/article-5131-1.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Linux下最为人熟知的归档/压缩工具</a> 这篇文章并在其基础上进行了补充。</p><hr><h1 id="tar"><a href="#tar" class="headerlink" title="tar"></a>tar</h1><p>: 衍生自”Tape archiver”, 最初被用来在磁带上归档和存储文件。在创建归档文件时， Tar可以保持原有文件和目录结构不变。</p><ol><li>创建归档(c / –create)  </li></ol><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># tar --create --verbose --file=archive.tar file1 file2 file3  </span><br><span class="line">tar cvf archive.tar file1 file2 file3</span><br><span class="line"># v选项代表显示压缩的细节</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li><p>列出归档文件内容(t / –list)  </p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tar --list archive.tar</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>提取归档(x / –extract)</p></li></ol><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tar xvf archive.tar</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>对归档文件进行更新(u /  –update)</li></ol><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tar uvf archive.tar newfile.c  </span><br><span class="line"># 若归档的newfile.c要比先前已经归档的新，则添加更新的newfile.c到归档里面。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>从归档中删除文件(–delete)  </li></ol><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tar --delete -f archive.tar file1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>“xxx.tar.*” 格式文件的压缩与解压<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tar -zcvf xxx.tar.gz file file1</span><br><span class="line">tar -xf xxx.tar.gz</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">tar -jcvf xxx.tar.bz2 file file1</span><br><span class="line">tar -xf xxx.tar.bz2</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">tar -Jcvf xxx.tar.xz file file1</span><br><span class="line">tar -Jxf xxx.tar.xz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><hr><h1 id="Gzip-Gunzip"><a href="#Gzip-Gunzip" class="headerlink" title="Gzip / Gunzip"></a>Gzip / Gunzip</h1><p>：压缩文件后缀”*.gz”.</p><ol><li>压缩文件  </li></ol><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">gzip file(s)  </span><br><span class="line"># 每个文件将被单独压缩，且源文件会被删除，可用-c选项来保留，如 ：  </span><br><span class="line">gzip -c file &gt; file.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>检查压缩比  </li></ol><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">gzip -l file.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>解压文件</li></ol><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">gunzip -c file.gz</span><br><span class="line"># (-c选项用来保留原文件)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h1 id="Bzip2-Bunzip2"><a href="#Bzip2-Bunzip2" class="headerlink" title="Bzip2 / Bunzip2"></a>Bzip2 / Bunzip2</h1><p>：压缩文件后缀名为”.bz2”，与gzip相比，能将文件压缩到更小，但运行速度比gzip慢</p><ol><li>压缩文件  </li></ol><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">bzip2 file1 file2 file3</span><br><span class="line">(每个文件单独被压缩)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>解压（用-d选项或bunzip2）  </li></ol><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">bzip2 -d file1.bz2</span><br><span class="line">bunzip2 file2.bz2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h1 id="7-zip"><a href="#7-zip" class="headerlink" title="7-zip"></a>7-zip</h1><p>：开源压缩软件。使用7z这种新的压缩格式，支持高压缩比。归档文件后缀”.7z”。支持 7Z, ZIP, Zip64, CAB, RAR（需要安装包p7zip-rar）, ARJ, GZIP, BZIP2, TAR, CRIO, RPM, ISO, DEB 压缩文件格式</p><ol><li>创建归档</li></ol><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">7zr a archive-name.7z file-name(s) / directory-name(s)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>列出归档包含文件</li></ol><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">7zr l archive-name.7z</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>提取归档文件</li></ol><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">7zr e archive-name.7z</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>更新归档文件</li></ol><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">7zr u archive-name.7z new-file</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>从归档文件中删除文件</li></ol><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">7zr d archive-name.7z file</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h1 id="rar-unrar"><a href="#rar-unrar" class="headerlink" title="rar / unrar"></a>rar / unrar</h1><p>：支持’rar’格式压缩/解压缩。</p><ol><li><p>压缩文件</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 先安装包支持</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install rar</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install unrar</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">rar a achive.rar file file1</span><br><span class="line"># 可在achive.rar基础上继续添加</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>删除归档中的文件</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rar d achive.rar file</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>抽取归档中的文件</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rar e achive.rar file1</span><br><span class="line"># 抽取的文件在当前目录中</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>解压文件</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rar e achive.rar</span><br><span class="line">unrar e achive.rar</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><hr><h1 id="zip-unzip"><a href="#zip-unzip" class="headerlink" title="zip / unzip"></a>zip / unzip</h1><p>: 支持“zip”格式压缩/解压缩.</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 先安装包支持</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install zip</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install unzip</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 将所有file*.doc 的文件打包成zip文件</span><br><span class="line">zip achive.zip file*.doc</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 删除achive.zip中指定文件</span><br><span class="line">zip -d achive.zip file1.doc</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 添加一个文件</span><br><span class="line">zip -g achive.zip file1.doc</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 需要压缩目录时，用-r选项</span><br><span class="line">zip -r achive.zip dir</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
